page.title: 14SUNDAY CONTRASTS
page.content: Lynne Ruth Douglas Scott saw baby Gavin christened at church _______ Melanie Beverley Andrew-John went to South Church Sunday School Picnic at Kirriemuir.They took part in a treasure hunt and ran races. _______ Hamish,his dad and Innes took part in a 3 mile fun run. _______ Gavin swam in the A Championships _______ Stuart attended a Pageant Rehearsal _______ Kirsty cleaned out the rabbit hutch _______ Aislinn read the Cartoons in the Mail _______ Others went for picnics.Others played golf.Others just sunbathed and tanned _______
